version_description: Playable and complete version / suggestions for playable voicings.
This is the only capo 4 version that uses simple chords and also actually sounds like the song.
A simpler way of playing it, a few more accurate chords and better formatting.
A correct tab I think. And laid out pretty darn good :).
This version differs from previous versions, in that it extends the range of chords and includes the lead accent riffs.
